            1
          
        
        <
        
          i
          
            2
          
        
        <
        ⋯
        <
        
          i
          
            k
          
        
        ≤
        n
      
    
    {\displaystyle I=(i_{1},i_{2},\ldots ,i_{k}),1\leq i_{1}<i_{2}<\cdots <i_{k}\leq n}
  , we define 
  
    
      
        d
        
          x
          
            I
          
        
        :=
        d
        
          x
          
            
              i
              
